org.apache.soap.rpc
Class Parameter

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--org.apache.soap.rpc.Parameter
public class Parameter
extends java.lang.Object

A Parameter represents an argument to an RPC call. Parameter objects are used by both the client and the server.
